ygData.messageBody:
U r welcome LKW, Wish i could do more. Im a lvl 9 monk and have less than 1
plat in the bank .*sob*sob.*
Gary got me netted gloves b4. he's my hero ;)

I saw Yukata on my list last nite but b4 if could msg him. he was gone. :(

Lvl 1- 4 , i think will be spending time on bats and spiders stuff. it
boring after a while but hang on, the world opens up when u get to higher
lvl and team play.
The interative elements like Fishing and talking is just as fun as trying to
reach the next Lvl fast (powerLeveling). Eq is more than just power Leveling
, sometimes i spend time helping others in a team, other times on enchaning
the skills likeTaloring.

Wilson , i heard Qeynos has a good hunting ground, maybe i should make my
way there someday but i probably wont survive the jorney.lol

cya guys in EQ
